<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Order Confirmation</title>
    <style>
        /* General styling */
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        h1 {
            color: #333;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 24px;
        }
        p {
            color: #555;
            line-height: 1.5;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin: 10px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        /* Order details styling */
        .order-details {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .order-details span {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #333;
        }
        /* Footer note */
        .footer-note {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #888;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Order Confirmation</h1>
        <p>Thank you for your purchase!</p>
        <p>Hello <%= user.name %>,</p>
        <p>Your order for the course <strong><%= order.name %></strong> has been successfully processed.</p>

        <div class="order-details">
            <p>Order ID: <span><%= order._id %></span></p>
            <p>Course Name: <span><%= order.name %></span></p>
            <p>Price: <span>Rp <%= order.price.toLocaleString("id-ID") %></span></p>
            <p>Date: <span><%= order.date %></span></p>
        </div>

        <p>We're excited to have you onboard. Happy learning!</p>

        <div class="footer-note">Â© Belaja - All rights reserved</div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
